    "description": {
      "content": "The Wolfram|Alpha Short Answers API returns a single concise plain-text answer from Wolfram|Alpha. Designed for chatbots, mobile apps, smartwatches, and any context requiring brief factual responses. Returns HTTP 501 when no sufficiently short answer is available.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Wolfram|Alpha Developer Support",
